akatea
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:[Ma. /akatea/ W.6 Akatea ... Metrosideros albifloraand M. perforata, climbing plants (Maori aka + tea white).][Phs main def as above should go to white rata, and simple def. here.] Metrosideros spp., esp. M. perforata (in SI M.diffusa), a vine with small white flowers. See white (flowering) rata.
